data.description: NEW PRICE!!! BRAND NEW ROOF NOVEMBER 2023 and NEW CARPET IN ALL BEDROOMS....  Welcome Home to this adorable 3 Bedroom/2 Bath that is located in South Lakeland's Krenson Woods! Open Floor plan with Roomy Kitchen and Open Living area! High ceilings, sliding glass doors that open to private fenced in back yard for entertaining. Kitchen has solid  wood cabinetry, center island to make cooking and entertaining a breeze and a closet pantry.  Master Bedroom has large walk in closet.  Master Bath boast of tiled floors with Spacious Garden Tub and a separate stand up shower. Community playground area with picnic tables for the family. Check out the paid for solar panels on the home, which will save you cash on your electric bill while helping the environment. Conveniently located between Tampa and Orlando!  Minutes to Polk Parkway. MAKE YOUR APPMNT TODAY.
